HEADWORD: Bovinae
<hw>Bovinae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a term essentially coextensive with
the genus <gen>Bos</gen>, including cattle, buffalo, and sometimes kudu;
-- it is not used technically.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> subfamily Bovinae.</syn>⟦br⟧
